text: Marinella Panayiotou (; born 4 October 1995) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a forward for AC Omonia and the Cyprus women's national team. ==Club career== On 23 August 2016, Panayiotou joined Barcelona FA. Two years later, she moved to AC Omonia. ==International career== Panayiotou capped for Cyprus at senior level during the 2017 Aphrodite Cup, including a 1–2 loss to Latvia on 12 March 2017. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers Category:AC Omonia players Category:Barcelona FA players
